esterlands\">From the Westerlands</span></h4>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\"><img alt=\"House Lannister.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/20px-House_Lannister.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/30px-House_Lannister.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/40px-House_Lannister.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lyman_Lannister\" title=\"Lyman Lannister\">Lyman Lannister</a>\n<ul><li>Three hundred knights from <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a></li></ul></li></ul>\n<h4><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"From_the_North\">From the North</span></h4>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\"><img alt=\"House Stark.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/20px-House_Stark.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/30px-House_Stark.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/40px-House_Stark.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Brandon_Stark_(father_of_Walton)\" title=\"Brandon Stark (father of Walton)\">Brandon Stark</a>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\"><img alt=\"House Stark.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/20px-House_Stark.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/30px-House_Stark.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/40px-House_Stark.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Walton_Stark_(son_of_Brandon)\" title=\"Walton Stark (son of Brandon)\">Walton Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\"><img alt=\"House Stark.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/20px-House_Stark.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/30px-House_Stark.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/40px-House_Stark.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Alaric_Stark\" title=\"Alaric Stark\">Alaric Stark</a></li></ul></li>\n<li>A dozen northern <a href=\"/index.php/Bannermen\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bannermen\">bannermen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\"><img alt=\"Night&#39;s Watch.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/20px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/30px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/40px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Thirty sworn brothers of the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a></li></ul>\n<h4><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Foreigners\">Foreigners</span></h4>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\"><img alt=\"House Martell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/20px-House_Martell.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/30px-House_Martell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/40px-House_Martell.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Sister of the <a href=\"/index.php/Prince_of_Dorne\" title=\"Prince of Dorne\">Prince of Dorne</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\"><img alt=\"Braavos.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/20px-Braavos.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/30px-Braavos.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a2/Braavos.svg/40px-Braavos.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Son of the <a href=\"/index.php/Sealord_of_Braavos\" title=\"Sealord of Braavos\">Sealord of Braavos</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\"><img alt=\"Tyrosh.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d7/Tyrosh.svg/20px-Tyrosh.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d7/Tyrosh.svg/30px-Tyrosh.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d7/Tyrosh.svg/40px-Tyrosh.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Archon_of_Tyrosh#Jaehaerys_I\" title=\"Archon of Tyrosh\">Archon of Tyrosh</a> and his <a href=\"/index.php/Archon%27s_daughter_(Jaehaerys_I)\" title=\"Archon&#39;s daughter (Jaehaerys I)\">daughter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\"><img alt=\"Pentos.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/01/Pentos.svg/20px-Pentos.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/01/Pentos.svg/30px-Pentos.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/01/Pentos.svg/40px-Pentos.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Twenty-two <a href=\"/index.php/Magisters\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Magisters\">magisters</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Golden_Wedding&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Never has there been such a glory in all the annals of <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;writings of <a href=\"/index.php/Benifer\" title=\"Benifer\">Benifer</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Golden_Wedding&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]